00:00:00,090 --> 00:00:06,860
Cambodia plans to restore its train lines, which could mean the end of the famous bamboo trains.

2
00:00:07,800 --> 00:00:13,650
The homemade trains, known as ‘norries’, are powered by small motorcycle engines.

3
00:00:14,460 --> 00:00:17,310
They can carry as many as 15 people.

4
00:00:18,450 --> 00:00:23,160
There are 40 norry drivers who have been working at the tracks for 20 years.

5
00:00:24,585 --> 00:00:30,015
With the tracks gone, they do not know how they will eat or care for their families.

6
00:00:31,005 --> 00:00:36,375
They are appealing to the government to find another place to run the norries.

